rows.label: tlk70000019_05_msg0001
rows.name:
My idiot of a husband really owes
you one.

rows.label: tlk70000019_05_msg0002
rows.name:
What's more, I'm surprised you
managed to find him so easily!

rows.label: tlk70000019_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh? He was exactly where I said he'd
be? Whether I'm happy about it or not,
I guess I do know him pretty well.

rows.label: tlk70000019_05_msg0004
rows.name: Aw, stop! You'll make me blush!
